						<summary>

						<p>Slab fixed in the south-east corner of the second landing on the Mallikārjuna temple to the Kanakadurgā temple.</p>						

						<p>Vishṇuvardhana, 17th year.</p>						

						<p>States that one Chaṭṭapa consecrated the image of Pārthīśvara on the Indrakīla hill by the grace of Vishṇuvardhana, son of Vikramāditya. Published: <hi rend="italic">S.I.I.,</hi> Vol. X, No. 16.</p>						

